@ChatAI_HostAddress = https://localhost:7130

### Non-streaming chat
POST {{ChatAI_HostAddress}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What is the capital of France?",
  "history": null
}

###

### Non-streaming chat — multi-turn with history
POST {{ChatAI_HostAddress}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "And what about Germany?",
  "history": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "contents": [{ "kind": 1, "text": "What is the capital of France?" }]
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "contents": [{ "kind": 1, "text": "The capital of France is Paris." }]
    }
  ]
}

###

### Streaming chat (SSE — use curl or EventSource, not the .http runner)
# curl -kN -X POST https://localhost:7130/api/chat/stream \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -H "Accept: text/event-stream" \
#   -d '{"message":"Tell me a short story about a robot."}'
POST {{ChatAI_HostAddress}}/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": "Tell me a short story about a robot.",
  "history": null
}

###

### OpenAPI spec (dev only)
GET {{ChatAI_HostAddress}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

###

### Weather forecast (sample endpoint)
GET {{ChatAI_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

